title: Jewel_Quest_III_Portable
description:
Jewel Quest III

Rupert and Emma have decided to open a Museum. Their daughter Natalie is infected by spores while playing 
with a jewel board. Ultimately, Rupert hopes to find a cure for Natalie and find the fabled Golden Jewel Board, 
an artifact that is only rumored to exist. During his travels, Rupert receives cryptic messages from someone 
who claims to hold the cure for Natalie. Who will it be? Find out in part three of the ultimate jewel matching 
series!
